opendial.inference.queries

Class Query

  • java.lang.Object
    • opendial.inference.queries.Query
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ProbQuery, UtilQuery

    public abstract class Query
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class representing a generic inference query. Each query is composed of a Bayesian network, a set of query variables, and some evidence.
    Version:
    $Date:: 2014-01-30 22:55:33 #$
    Author:
    Pierre Lison (plison@ifi.uio.no)
